---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Tooth-Colored Fillings in Footscray | Natural-Looking Dental Restorations"
  description="Restore decayed or damaged teeth with tooth-colored fillings from Top Dentists Footscray. Our composite fillings blend seamlessly with your natural teeth, offering a durable and aesthetically pleasing solution."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Fillings</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Tooth-Colored Fillings
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Fillings are necessary when a tooth is affected by decay, cracks, or fractures. At Top Dentists Footscray, we use tooth-colored composite fillings to restore damaged teeth while maintaining a natural appearance.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              A white composite filling is used to repair a tooth that is affected by decay, cracks, fractures, etc. Because composite fillings are white, they can be closely matched to the color of existing teeth. Composites are very durable and will last many years, giving you a long-lasting, beautiful smile.
            </p>

            <!-- Filling Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                The Filling Procedure
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Removing decay</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The decayed or affected portion of the tooth is carefully removed to prepare the area for filling.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Color matching</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The composite resin material is carefully selected to match your existing tooth color for a seamless appearance.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Layered application</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The composite material is applied in layers and hardened with a special curing light.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Shaping and polishing</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The filling is shaped to restore the tooth's natural contours and polished for a smooth finish.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits of Composite Fillings -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Benefits of Our Composite Fillings
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Durable</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Long-lasting results that withstand daily wear</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Natural-looking</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Seamless color blend with your natural teeth</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Metal-free</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Mercury-free composition for your peace of mind</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Conservative</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Preserves more of your natural tooth structure</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Comparison -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                Why Choose Composite Over Amalgam?
              </h3>
              
              <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-sm text-left">
                  <thead class="text-xs text-neutral-700 uppercase bg-neutral-50">
                    <tr>
                      <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3">Feature</th>
                      <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3">Composite (White)</th>
                      <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3">Amalgam (Silver)</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr class="bg-white border-b">
                      <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-neutral-900">
                        Appearance
                      </th>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-green-600">Natural tooth color</td>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-600">Visible silver color</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="bg-neutral-50 border-b">
                      <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-neutral-900">
                        Mercury Content
                      </th>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-green-600">Mercury-free</td>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-600">Contains mercury</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="bg-white border-b">
                      <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-neutral-900">
                        Tooth Structure
                      </th>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-green-600">Preserves more tooth</td>
                      <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-600">Requires more removal</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Care Instructions -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Caring for Your Fillings
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Maintain good oral hygiene</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Regular dental check-ups and cleanings</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Avoid excessive force when chewing</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Don't use teeth as tools</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Filling Longevity
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    5-15 years
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    With proper care, composite fillings can last many years, providing excellent function and appearance.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Need Natural-Looking Fillings?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Don't let tooth damage compromise your smile. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          for tooth-colored composite fillings
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>